  "texts": [
    "Orthopedic education, like all medical fields, places an emphasis on evidence-based practice.",
    "Generative AI tools can help with this process by providing concise summary of clinical trials and critical practice guidelines [74,85].",
    "For instance, entering the prompt \"What are the clinical implications of the American College of Rheumatology guidelines for osteoarthritis?\"",
    "into ChatGPT can yield a concise, pointby-point response.",
    "This would highlight key practice implications such as non-pharmacologic interventions, pharmacologic treatments, surgical options, and adjunctive therapies recommended for managing osteoarthritis."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Generative AI tools can help with this process by providing concise summary of clinical trials and critical practice guidelines [74,85]."
  ]
